snippet.textDisplay:
Original (Urdu)

Aye rah e haq kay shaheedoun
Wafa ki tasweeroun
Tumhain watan ki hawaein salam kehti hain
Aye rah e haq kay shaheedoun
Allahu
Laganay aag jo aye thay ashiyaanoun ko
Woh sholay apnay lahoo say bujha diyaye tu nain
Bacha liya hai yateemi say kitnay phooloun ko
Suhaag kitni baharoun kay rakh liyaye tu nain
Tumhain chaman ki fazaein salam kehti hain
Aye rah e haq kay shaheedoun 
Chalay jo ho gay shahadat ka jaam pi kar tum
Rasul pak nain bahoun main lay liya ho ga
Ali tumhari shujahat pai jhoomtay houn gau
Hussein pak nain yeh irshaad kiya ho ga
Tumhain khuda ki razaein salam kehti hain hain
Aye rah e haq kay shaheedoun

English

O Martyrs of the Path of Justice!
Models of Loyalty!
The Winds of the Nation greet you,
O Martyrs of the Path of Justice
God is
You extinguished the Sparks that came to set alight our tents with your blood,
How many flowers have you rescued from Orphanhood,
How many mournings of the Moonsoons have you prevented,
The winds of the nation greet you,
O Martyrs of the Path of Justice!
When you set out ,having drunk from the Goblet of Martyrdom,
The Pure Messenger must have welcomed you to his arms,
Ali must have been ecstatic at your Bravery,
Hussein must have said ,
"The Approval of God greets you"
O Martyrs of the Path of Justice.
